caplog.set_level(logging.INFO)
m.get('https://ovalmoney.com/user?key1=value1&key2=value2&key2=value3',
    json={'test': True}, headers={'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
    status_code=200)
s = Session()
response = s.get('https://ovalmoney.com/user', params={'key1': 'value1',
    'key2': ['value2', 'value3']})
assert response.headers
assert response.status_code == 200
assert response.json() == {'test': True}
